ityWarningCount} 个安全警告","policyContainsWarning":"您的策略包含 {warningCount} 个警告","filterActions":"搜索操作","clearFilterActions":"清除筛选条件并显示服务的所有操作","filterServices":"搜索服务","clearFilterServices":"清除筛选条件并显示所有可用服务","matches":"{count} 个匹配项","learnMoreAboutValidation":"了解有关策略验证的更多信息","clearSearchLabel":"清除"},"whatsNewWidget":{"features.iam":"{\\"feature0\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon Bedrock introduces API keys for streamlined development\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/07/amazon-bedrock-api-keys-for-streamlined-development\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"07/08/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-07-08T19:34:00Z\\"}, \\"feature1\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS Service Reference Information now supports annotations for service actions\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/06/aws-service-reference-information-annotations/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"06/26/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-06-26T10:00:00-07:00\\"}, \\"feature2\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS expands resource control policies (RCPs) support to two additional services\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/06/aws-resource-control-policies-additional-services\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"06/19/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-06-19T13:00:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature3\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS IAM now enforces MFA for root users across all account types\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/06/aws-iam-mfa-root-users-across-all-account-types/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"06/17/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-06-17T10:00:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature4\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon EKS Pod Identity simplifies the experience for cross-account access\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/06/amazon-eks-pod-identity-cross-account-access\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"06/12/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-06-12T13:00:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature5\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon EBS now supports additional resource-level permissions for copying EBS snapshots\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/04/amazon-ebs-additional-resource-level-permissions-copying-eb-snapshots\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"04/22/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-04-22T15:15:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature6\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS Identity and Access Management now supports dual-stack (IPv4 and IPv6) environments\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/03/aws-identity-access-management-dual-stack-ipv4-ipv6-environments\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"03/28/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-03-28T16:40:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature7\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS Service Reference Information now supports resources and condition keys\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/03/aws-service-reference-information-resources-condition-keys\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"03/13/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-03-13T13:00:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature8\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"IAM Access Analyzer now supports Internet Protocol Version 6 (IPv6)\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/03/iam-access-analyzer-supports-ipv6/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"03/05/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-03-05T10:00:00-08:00\\"}, \\"feature9\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon RDS now provides visibility into IAM DB Authentication metrics and logs\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/02/amazon-rds-visibility-iam-db-authentication-metrics-logs\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"02/26/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-02-26T17:00:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature10\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon ECS adds support for additional IAM condition keys\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/02/amazon-ecs-additional-iam-condition-keys\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"02/26/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-02-26T13:00:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature11\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS IAM announces support for encrypted SAML assertions \\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/02/aws-iam-encrypted-saml-assertions/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"02/05/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-02-05T10:00:00-08:00\\"}, \\"feature12\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS CodeBuild announces support for project ARN and build ARN IAM condition keys\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2025/01/aws-codebuild-project-arn-build-arn-iam-condition-keys\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"01/28/2025\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2025-01-28T16:50:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature13\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"IAM Roles Anywhere credential helper now supports TPM 2.0\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/12/iam-roles-anywhere-credential-helper-tpm-2-0\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"12/17/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-12-17T14:50:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature14\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Announcing AWS STS support for ECDSA-based signatures of OIDC tokens\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/aws-sts-ecdsa-based-signatures-oidc-tokens\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/22/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-22T15:15:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature15\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon EKS simplifies providing IAM permissions to EKS add-ons\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/amazon-eks-iam-permissions-eks-add-ons\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/18/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-18T17:00:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature16\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Centrally manage root access in AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM)\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/manage-root-access-aws-identity-access-management/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/15/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-15T10:00:00-08:00\\"}, \\"feature17\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Customize scope of IAM Access Analyzer unused access analysis  \\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/customize-scope-iam-access-analyzer-unused-access-analysis/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/14/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-14T10:00:00-08:00\\"}, \\"feature18\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Introducing resource control policies (RCPs) to centrally restrict access to AWS resources\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/resource-control-policies-restrict-access-aws-resources/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/13/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-13T10:00:00-08:00\\"}, \\"feature19\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS IAM now supports PrivateLink in the AWS GovCloud (US) Regions\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/11/aws-iam-privatelink-govcloud-us-regions\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"11/08/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-11-08T13:00:00-05:00\\"}, \\"feature20\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Streamline automation of policy management workflows with service reference information\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/10/streamline-automation-policy-management-workflows-service-reference-information\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"10/10/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-10-10T13:00:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature21\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"Amazon S3 Access Grants introduce the ListCallerAccessGrants API\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/09/amazon-s3-access-grants-listcalleraccessgrants-api\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"09/05/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-09-05T17:50:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature22\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS Identity and Access Management now supports AWS PrivateLink in all commercial Regions\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/08/aws-identity-access-management-aws-privatelink-regions/\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"08/22/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-08-22T10:00:00-07:00\\"}, \\"feature23\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS Identity and Access Management simplifies management of OpenID Connect identity providers\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/07/aws-identity-access-management-open-id-connect-identity-providers\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"07/12/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-07-12T16:30:00-04:00\\"}, \\"feature24\\": {\\"headline\\": \\"AWS IAM Access Analyzer now offers policy checks for public and critical resource access\\", \\"headlineUrl\\": \\"/about-aws/whats-new/2024/06/aws-iam-access-analyzer-policy-checks\\", \\"postDateTime\\": \\"06/11/2024\\", \\"absoluteDateTime\\": \\"2024-06-11T08:00:00-04:00\\"}}","today":" 今天","yesterday":" 昨天","daysAgo":" {day} 天前","weekAgo":" 1 周前","weeksAgo":" {week} 周前","monthAgo":" 1 个月前","monthsAgo":" {month} 个月前","yearAgo":" 1 年前","header":"新增内容","description":"IAM 中的功能更新","viewAll":"查看所有","viewAllAria":"查看有关新增内容的所有信息","more":"更多","less":"更少","moreAria":"显示更多结果","lessAria":"显示更少结果"},"mfaListWidget":{"mfaListLoadingText":"正在加载","mfaListTableHeader":"多重身份验证（MFA）","mfaListTableHeaderDescription":"请使用 MFA 来提高 AWS 环境的安全性，这是最佳实践。登录受 MFA 保护的账户需要用户名、密码和来自 MFA 设备的身份验证码。","remove":"删除","resync":"重新同步","assignMfa":"分配 MFA","noDevice":"没有 MFA 设备","noDeviceDescription":"添加 MFA 设备以提高 AWS 环境的安全性","deleteMFAModal":"是否删除 MFA 设备？","deleteMFAContent":"他们登录时无需提供 MFA 代码。","cancel":"取消","resyncMFATitle":"重新同步 MFA 设备","resyncMFAContent":"填写来自 MFA 设备的两个连续代码以将其重新同步。","resyncInput1":"MFA 代码 1","resyncInput2":"MFA 代码 2"},"selectMFADevice":{"virtualDesc":"使用移动设备或电脑上安装的应用程序生成的代码进行身份验证。","u2fDesc":"使用通过触摸 YubiKey 或其他支持的 U2F 设备来生成的代码进行身份验证。","hardwareDesc":"使用硬件“基于时间的一次性密码”（TOTP）令牌上显示的代码进行身份认证。","authenticatorApp":"身份验证器应用程序","u2fSecurityKey":"U2F 安全密钥","hardwareDevice":"硬件 TOTP 令牌","selectDevice":"选择 MFA 设备","selectDeviceSmall":"需要进行身份验证时，除用户名和密码外，还要选择要使用的 MFA 设备。","cancel":"取消","next":"下一步"},"setupMFADevice":{"pageTitle":"激活多重身份验证（MFA）","setupTitle":"设置您的身份验证器应用程序","virtualDesc":"虚拟 MFA 设备是在您的设备上运行的应用程序，您可以扫描 QR 代码对其进行配置。","install":"在您的移动设备或计算机上安装 Google Authenticator、Duo Mobile 或 Authy 等兼容的应用程序。","list":"查看兼容应用程序的列表","show":"显示 QR 代码","step2Text":"打开身份验证器应用程序，选择此页面上的<b>显示 QR 代码</b>，然后使用该应用程序扫描该代码。或者，您可以键入密钥。<show>显示密钥</show>","step3Text":"在下面键入两个连续的 MFA 代码","code1":"在下面输入虚拟应用程序的代码","code2":"等待 30 秒，然后输入第二个代码条目。","cancel":"取消","previous":"上一步","addMFA":"添加 MFA","hardwareTitle":"设置硬件 MFA 设备","hardwareDescription":"有关如何使用硬件 MFA 设备的更多信息，请参阅 <a>IAM 用户指南</a>","hardwareLabel1":"输入位于设备背面的设备序列号。","hardwareLabel2":"按下设备正面的按钮，然后输入显示的 6 位数字。","hardwareLabel3":"等待 30 秒，然后再次按下按钮。输入第二个数字。","serialNumber":"序列号","MFACode1":"MFA 代码 1","MFACode2":"MFA 代码 2","u2fTitle":"设置安全密钥","u2fDesc":"支持的使用安全密钥的配置","u2fStep1":"将您的安全密钥连接到您的设备。","u2fStep2":"点击安全密钥。","passkeySetupTitle":"通行密钥或安全密钥","passkeySetupDesc":"通行密钥使您能够使用指纹、面部、设备 PIN 码或 FIDO2 安全密钥安全地登录您的 AWS 账户。","passkeySetupStep1Label":"第 1 步（共 2 步）","passkeySetupStep1":"在此设备上创建通行密钥，或者如果您使用其他设备，请立即连接。","passkeySetupStep2Label":"第 2 步（共 2 步）","passkeySetupStep2":"按照浏览器中的说明进行操作。","passkeySetupLoading":"正在加载","waiting":"正在等待安全密钥...","tap":"点击密钥","troubleShoot":"对 MFA 进行问题排查","u2fComplete":"此 U2F 安全密钥的设置已完成","u2fCompleteText":"现在必须点击此 U2F 安全密钥才能登录。","done":"已完成","wizardStep1Title":"选择 MFA 设备","wizardStep2Title":"设置设备","optional":"可选","next":"下一步","retry":"重试","selectVirtualDesc":"使用移动设备或电脑上安装的应用程序生成的代码进行身份验证。","selectU2fDesc":"使用通过触摸 YubiKey 或其他支持的 FIDO 安全密钥来生成的代码进行身份验证。","selectPasskeyDesc":"使用指纹、面部或屏幕锁进行身份验证。在此设备上创建通行密钥，或使用其他设备，如 FIDO2 安全密钥。","hardwareDesc":"使用硬件“基于时间的一次性密码”（TOTP）令牌上显示的代码进行身份认证。","selectHardwareOtherDeviceDesc":"使用硬件 TOTP 令牌或其他硬件设备生成的代码进行身份验证。","otherDesc":"使用 Gemalto 令牌上显示的代码进行身份验证。","authenticatorApp":"身份验证器应用程序","u2fSecurityKey":"U2F 安全密钥","hardwareDevice":"硬件 TOTP 令牌","selectDevice":"选择 MFA 设备","selectDeviceSmall":"需要进行身份验证时，除用户名和密码外，还要选择要使用的 MFA 设备。","deviceSelectionLabel":"设备选项","deviceSelectionDescription":"除了用户名和密码外，您还将使用此设备对您的账户进行身份验证。","displayNameLabel":"通行密钥显示名称","displayNameDescription":"使用通行密钥登录时将显示此名称。如果需要，可以自定义默认的建议名称。","displayNameDefaultSelection":"使用默认的通行密钥显示名称","displayNameConstraintText":"最多 64 个字符。有效字符：A-Z、a-z、0-9 和 + = , . @ _ -（连字符）","displayNameLengthErrorText":"通行密钥显示名称不能超过 64 个字符","displayNameRequiredErrorText":"通行密钥显示名称为必填项","displayNameInvalidCharactersErrorText":"无效字符。使用有效字符：A-Z、a-z、0-9 和 + = , . @ _ -（连字符）","stepNumber":"步骤 {stepNumber}","stepLabel":"步骤 {stepNumber}，共 {stepCount} 个步骤","in